column5: I like Rons  Dear God, All I ask for in 2011 is a big, fat bank account and a slim body, please don’t mix these up like you did last year. Amen.

I don't understand why this thread had no hits???? Great topic IMO.  Here is one I just came across that I feel is great...   Never under estimate overwhelming stupidity in overwhelming numbers.    This ones killer too!

I have a lot of people who expect me to magically appear whenever there is a need of a hand or a handyman or ...?  Somedays it's impossible to cover all the bases and I often hear about how they looked for me but couldn't find me.  One day out of frustration I just up and quipped that I probably wasn't where they were looking and it kinda stuck.  Not the greatest story, but true for sure!  Michael
HERES MY NEW ONE ......... just because the phones ringing dose'nt mean i have to anwser it !
i just tried to squash that little bugger on my screen
Good One!  Think I'll change my voicemail message to something like that.  Michael
Why tanks Brian.  I have got a few more in the fire, just waiting for a reason to bring them up.
Heard this while watching a UK fishing video...  "Fishing"...an excuse for being there...  You can have it if'n you so choose...

Sry Ron,you just dropped to second.  I will be as harsh as truth, and uncompromising as justice... I am in earnest, I will not equivocate, I will not excuse, I will not retreat a single inch, and I will be heard.”
